games/gamez includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/%%PORTNAME%%

TO START GAMEZ ON BOOT:
echo 'gamez_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/%%PORTNAME%% start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8085/

